list	[1, 2, 3]	Ordered, mutable collection
tuple	(1, 2, 3)	Ordered, immutable list
dict	{"a": 1}	Key-value pairs
set	{1, 2, 3}	Unique, unordered collection
None	None	Represents "nothing"

ğŸ” 5. Control Flow
âœ… if, elif, else
